metadata.name: TH***
metadata.description:
TH*** is the third part of "Life Algorithmic" collection.

An exploration of change and stagnation observed in those seeking the betterment of fortune only to be stuck on the way.
They were witnessed too late.
Forced to leave their home only to never fully reach another.
Dedicated to those who were lost on the journey.
These algorithmic art pieces attempt to capture a conceptualization of the souls, bodies and thoughts of those who took the journey.

Format: MP4
Resolution: 2160x2160 Pixels
Length: 24 Sec loop
File size: 49.0 MB
